data.description: *Flowers Plantation* Fantastic 5 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath (5th bedroom could be used as a study or office). Home has been updated with gorgeous wide plank and tile flooring throughout! Gourmet kitchen with high end cabinetry soft to close and pull outs. Massive island with eat-in bar, granite countertops. Upstairs loft and large master with serene en-suite and large walk-in. Screened porch with grilling patio and fenced back yard. Close to Publix and Harris Teeter at 42 and Buffalo
